	EXPERIMENT 
**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************

Note: by default, this set-up runs 10 blocks in randomized order.
change /blocks = 
to change the number of blocks or the order of blocks that should be run
and than adapt the blocknumber of the "finish" block accordingly

<expt svt>
/ blocks = [
	1 = intro;
	2-11 = noreplace(domain1, domain2, domain3, domain4, domain5, domain6, domain7, domain8, domain9, domain10);
	12 = finish;
]
</expt>

<monkey>
/ latencydistribution = normal(4000, 500)
</monkey>

